PrecisOrder accepting a "DESIGNATION" duly approved by the TSUU T'INA NATION BAND OF INDIANS whereby the band conditionally surrenders some 70.8 hectares (175 acres) of land situate on SARCEE INDIAN RESERVE No. 145, in the Province of Alberta, for a term of seventy-five (75) years, so that they can be leased to third party interests for commercial purposes.
